{"tid":645502,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【正字】各位香港人留意番","createTime":"2018-04-28T07:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T11:43:51.000Z","uid":30006,"like":48,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a3336c387e818867ce2ceb9e3f57faccd6876e6d","tid":645502,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"1.返大陸<br />\n呢個係上一代遺留落黎，以前好多人偷渡，所以佢地家在中國，所以係用「返」。<br />\n如果你係97前英治香港出世土生土長，你應該用「去」。<br />\n<br />\n97後出世，用「去」都無錯，總係地理上看。"},{"pid":"0df0b82c6367859b6526ea08eef95eea4f2dac8f","tid":645502,"uid":30006,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:49:01.000Z","msg":"2.䌓體<br />\n中文本身係無䌓簡之分，而係因為本身要教育文盲而強行被「簡化」(破壞黎形容會貼切），所以「䌓」只係比一直學習殘體字的人用，只有佢地先會覺得「䌓」。<br />\n一直沿用「䌓體」的人，其實直接講中文就是，如果真係要區分，應該叫作「正體」中文，因殘體完全係無視漢字系統的法則隨意刪減，不能稱為簡化。"},{"pid":"1b2b24e14a499d5bb94917a3d479ddc82c18e786","tid":645502,"uid":30006,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"3.回歸<br />\n<br />\n呢個唔使多解釋。黃子華有講。同埋當年租借香港同共產黨無關。上手住戶借錢比你，之後搬左或失蹤，唔通你還錢比新租客？"},{"pid":"decf6151234dc17d43e14d8f0a33ac505ee62d84","tid":645502,"uid":30006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:31:59.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4e51f43298afb528bccea6f9fea09cfdbae67522","tid":645502,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f087d7fd521a5cc95cc7f18410b92e93ae5df658","tid":645502,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T09:55:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f1c74d94c0bddfd651544923020d3cf7bacef035","tid":645502,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"aef6bd944d7427cd1e986f649bce6ed1a71828af","tid":645502,"uid":56926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/